column5: Planning a spring trip to Temagami. Any info on lakeland airways out of Lake Temagami would be appreciated. Specifically Chris Willis lake. Thanks!

Jim, I am going to Lady Evelyn Lake this summer, while talking to the Lodge owner about other lakes to portage to he mentioned Chris Willis as one of the lakes I could walk in to. Did you know this lake could be accessed by other means that flying? I have never been to this lake, Just and FYI.
